statements: SELECT * FROM training_history;
SELECT model_name, accuracy, training_date FROM training_history WHERE accuracy > 0.8;
SELECT training_id, model_name, training_date, training_time FROM training_history ORDER BY training_date DESC;
SELECT model_name, loss FROM training_history WHERE model_name = 'svm';
SELECT training_id, model_name, accuracy FROM training_history WHERE loss < 0.1 ORDER BY accuracy DESC;
SELECT * FROM training_history WHERE accuracy > 0.9 ORDER BY training_date DESC, training_time DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT model_name, training_date, accuracy FROM training_history WHERE loss < 0.2 ORDER BY accuracy DESC;
SELECT model_name, training_date, training_time, loss FROM training_history WHERE model_name LIKE 'ResNet%' AND accuracy > 0.8;
SELECT model_name, training_date, accuracy FROM training_history WHERE training_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-28' ORDER BY accuracy DESC, training_date ASC;
SELECT model_name, loss, accuracy FROM training_history WHERE loss < 0.1 AND accuracy > 0.95 ORDER BY model_name ASC, accuracy DESC;
SELECT * FROM model_training_history;
SELECT model_name, training_accuracy, training_date FROM model_training_history ORDER BY training_date DESC;
SELECT model_name, training_accuracy FROM model_training_history WHERE training_accuracy > 0.9;
SELECT model_name, training_date, training_duration FROM model_training_history WHERE training_duration > '1 day'::INTERVAL;
SELECT model_name, training_accuracy, training_duration FROM model_training_history WHERE training_accuracy > 0.8 ORDER BY training_accuracy DESC;
SELECT model_name, training_date, training_accuracy FROM model_training_history WHERE model_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT model_id, model_name, training_date, training_accuracy FROM model_training_history WHERE training_accuracy >= 0.85 ORDER BY training_date DESC;

SELECT model_id, model_name, training_date, training_accuracy, loss_rate, prediction_accuracy, validation_accuracy FROM model_training_history JOIN performance_metrics ON model_training_history.model_id = performance_metrics.model_id WHERE training_accuracy > 0.8 AND prediction_accuracy > 0.75;
SELECT model_id, model_name, training_duration FROM model_training_history WHERE training_duration > '1 day' AND training_accuracy < 0.8;

SELECT model_name, training_accuracy, validation_accuracy FROM model_training_history JOIN performance_metrics ON model_training_history.model_id = performance_metrics.model_id WHERE training_accuracy < 0.75 OR validation_accuracy IS NULL;
SELECT * FROM model_training;
SELECT model_name, training_date, training_time FROM model_training WHERE training_id = 1;
SELECT model_name, training_date, training_time, loss FROM model_training WHERE loss > 0.2;
SELECT model_name, evaluation_date, precision, recall, f1_score FROM model_training JOIN evaluation_metrics ON model_training.training_id = evaluation_metrics.training_id;
SELECT model_name, training_date, training_time, loss, accuracy FROM model_training WHERE accuracy >= 0.85 AND training_duration < INTERVAL '1 hour';
SELECT * FROM model_training ORDER BY training_date DESC, training_time ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT model_name, training_date, loss FROM model_training WHERE accuracy > 0.8 AND loss < 0.5;
SELECT model_name, training_date, training_time, training_duration FROM model_training WHERE accuracy >= 0.9 ORDER BY training_date, training_time;
SELECT model_name, training_date, training_time, accuracy FROM model_training WHERE training_duration > INTERVAL '1 hour';

SELECT m.model_name, e.precision, e.recall, e.f1_score FROM model_training m JOIN evaluation_metrics e ON m.training_id = e.training_id WHERE e.precision > 0.7 AND e.recall > 0.6 ORDER BY e.f1_score DESC;
